HEADWORD: Navarino
<hw>Navarino</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>The name of a naval battle in
the War of Greek Independence (1827), at which the Turkish and Egyptian
fleet was defeated by the allied fleet.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> battle of Navarino.</syn>⟦br⟧
